	  under the terms of the GNU General Public License.
	  See http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.txt
snippet date
	`strftime("%Y-%m-%d")`
snippet email
	`g:myEmailAddress`
snippet name&email
	`g:myFullName` <${1:`g:myEmailAddress`}>${2}
snippet author
	${2}Author:	`g:myFullName` <${1:`g:myEmailAddress`}>${3}
snippet maintainer
	${2}Maintainer:	`g:myFullName` <${1:`g:myEmailAddress`}>${3}
snippet what
	`WhatString#Generate(exists('b:product') ? b:product : '${1:tools}')`
snippet So
	Stack Overflow
snippet Vim
	Vim version `Version()`
